    "Consequently, the density matrix diagonal for the massless case becomes ρ 1,1 (k 4) ∼ -2k 3 4 log (-k 4 η 0), (5.70) JHEP05(2024)196which contains the logarithmic term as typically expected for massless exchange [37].",
